        "subject": "LU-19749 ldiskfs: remove ubuntu18 patch series",
        "message": "LU-19749 ldiskfs: remove ubuntu18 patch series\n\nThe Ubuntu18.04 and earlier kernels are no longer supported.\n\nRemove the ldiskfs-4.15.0-*-ubuntu18.series file and all patches\nthat are no longer used by this (or other) patch series. The actual\npatches under ldiskfs/kernel_patches/patches/rhel7.x may still be\nreferenced by newer kernel series, so cannot be removed wholesale.\n\nThe ./contrib/scripts/clearpatches.sh ldiskfs/kernel_patches command\nwill report which patches are no longer used by any series file.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nChange-Id: I891467ecd392db3acefbd8b0cae3f40be43ebbe5\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/64109\nReviewed-by: Shaun Tancheff <shaun.tancheff@hpe.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Jian Yu <yujian@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: James Simmons <jsimmons@infradead.org>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
